reviewText: Great workout video, easy to understand and perform

This is a really good cardio workout. The problem I have is with the audio. Westfall does a live narration during the workout and with all the splashing noise, it's really hard to hear her instructions. She should've done a voice over. Her choice of music isn't the most inspiring either, but a great  improvement over the awful music in a couple of older Westfall DVDs I own.
Definitely gives you a workout. Your swimming pool needs options of deep water with some of the moves.
Easy to follow but very effective workout.
It is ok. But I just started. Did not relaise it was advanced. But will keep it and still use it

This is a serious workout. Karen keeps up the pace and makes great use of the pool. There is a paddle workout included but I use foam "weights" instead and they work great. I feel my strength improving and this has helped my weight loss efforts. I like that this a full hour, complete workout. I am eager for her next workout.
